infographic relation-dagre-flow-lr-compact-card
data
  title ranctl lifecycle
  desc Evidence stays explicit and verify can branch to steady state or rollback.
  nodes
    - id precheck
      label precheck
      desc Config, host, and policy checks
    - id plan
      label plan
      desc Render changes and rollback target
    - id approval
      label approval
      desc Explicit operator gate
    - id apply
      label apply
      desc Mutate runtime and persist state
    - id verify
      label verify
      desc Health checks and signatures
    - id observe
      label observe
      desc Steady state dashboard surface
    - id capture
      label capture-artifacts
      desc Logs, config, and evidence bundle
    - id rollback
      label rollback
      desc Restore target then verify again
  relations
    precheck -> plan
    plan -> approval
    approval -> apply
    apply -> verify
    verify -> observe
    verify -> capture
    capture -> rollback
theme
  palette #15803d #1d4ed8 #d97706 #ea580c #7c3aed #dc2626
  base
    text
      font-family Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui
